commit 5911991d81ec7b2cbd3603573cbdba525906236a
Author: Liew Rui Yan <aethernet65535@gmail.com>

mm/damon: add synchronous commit for commit_inputs

This patch makes the commit_inputs parameter of DAMON modules synchronous
by using damon_call(). It removes the asynchronous handle_commit_inputs()
and adds a new commit_inputs_store() callback to ensure validation errors
are immediately returned to userspace.

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/20260318153731.97470-1-aethernet65535@gmail.com

